557
00:32:30,800 --> 00:32:31,520
Shang Gu.

558
00:32:32,400 --> 00:32:32,830
Yue Mi.

559
00:32:33,430 --> 00:32:34,160
Shang Gu,

560
00:32:34,520 --> 00:32:36,000
