567
00:32:47,000 --> 00:32:47,560
Apa?

568
00:32:48,520 --> 00:32:50,430
Bagaimana roh primordialnya bisa
terluka parah sampai tak sadarkan diri?

569
00:32:51,000 --> 00:32:52,280
Di neraka terdalam,
aku berkali-kali menemui kesulitan,

570
00:32:52,400 --> 00:32:54,040
kekuatan roh-nyalah yang
selalu membantuku.

571
00:32:54,920 --> 00:32:55,800
Bai Jue ini...

572
00:32:56,310 --> 00:32:58,040
