616
00:34:20,470 --> 00:34:21,230
Baiklah.

617
00:34:34,600 --> 00:34:35,520
Suku Feniks…

618
00:34:38,430 --> 00:34:39,430
Maharani Feniks…

619
00:34:44,630 --> 00:34:45,710
Yue Mi…

