644
00:35:41,190 --> 00:35:42,470
Dia tidak berada di Istana Chaosheng.

645
00:35:43,320 --> 00:35:44,600
Jika kalian berani berbuat onar di sini,

646
00:35:45,120 --> 00:35:46,950
