00:36:02,710 --> 00:36:03,600
Mahadewa masih kecil,

655
00:36:03,760 --> 00:36:05,470
mementingkan hubungannya dengan
Dewa Sejati Tian Qi,

656
00:36:05,710 --> 00:36:06,870
